
Weather App is developed and operated by b3hzzzad. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your personal information while using our App.

Your Privacy Matters

We respect your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. We Do not collect any data.

App Usage Data: We collect information about how you interact with the App, such as your device type, operating system version, language preferences, and features you use. This helps us improve the App's functionality and user experience.
Location Data (Optional): If you choose to enable location-based features, we collect your approximate location (city or zip code) to provide you with localized weather forecasts. You can disable location sharing in your device settings or within the App at any time.
How We Use Your Information

We use the information we collect to:

Provide accurate and personalized weather forecasts based on your location or search queries.
Improve the App's features and functionality.
Understand how users interact with the App to make enhancements.
Send occasional push notifications about severe weather alerts (if enabled by you).
Respond to your inquiries and provide customer support.
Sharing Your Information

We do not share your personal information with any third parties for their own marketing or advertising purposes. We may share your information with the following limited exceptions:

Service Providers: We may share your information with third-party service providers who assist us in operating the App, such as cloud storage providers or analytics companies. These service providers are obligated to protect your information and use it only for the purposes we have authorized.
Legal Requirements: We may disclose your information if required by law or to comply with a legal process, such as a subpoena or court order.
Data Security

We are committed to protecting your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your information, including:

Secure data storage and transmission practices.
Regular security assessments and updates.
Access controls and restrictions on who can access your information.
Data Retention

We will retain your personal information for as long as you actively use our App or as needed to provide you with the services you requested. We will then delete your information unless required to retain it by law.

Your Choices

You have control over your personal information. You can:

Disable location sharing in your device settings or within the App.
Opt out of receiving push notifications by changing your App settings.
Request to access, update, or delete your personal information by contacting us.
Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at b3hzzzad@gmail.com.

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy on our website and within the App. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
